narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is your chance to develop an idea and make it happen with some degree of accountability. It can be lax or intense depending on how you treat it, but definitely worth it.

I would recommend it if your willing to really just work on one thing all semester. I liked that b/c I felt you really got it to a place you were proud of. But, if you get frustrated easy, then maybe this is not the course for you.
Stressful, but you learn a lot about yourself and about storytelling.
I would definitely recommend it. It's not very much work and is really interesting. Take it if you're interested in scene-writing or filmmaking.
